fields.name: ConsoleScreenshotBlobUri
fields.description: The console screenshot blob URI. **Note:** This will **not** be set if boot diagnostics is currently enabled with managed storage.

fields.name: SerialConsoleLogBlobUri
fields.description: The serial console log blob Uri. **Note:** This will **not** be set if boot diagnostics is currently enabled with managed storage.

fields.name: Status
fields.description: The boot diagnostics status information for the VM. **Note:** It will be set only if there are errors encountered in enabling boot diagnostics.
